{"tid":2081442,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Google轉軚 擬向傳媒買高質新聞","createTime":"2020-06-27T08:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T11:01:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0852d04ddbf1d838224e7028e6a7a00933f3e28d","tid":2081442,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200627/ZOE7GDZDP4XBNMC5Z6V5GIKAK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200627%2FZOE7GDZDP4XBNMC5Z6V5GIKAK4%2F&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=28a723a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200627%2FZOE7GDZDP4XBNMC5Z6V5GIKAK4%2F&h=7844e75e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200627/ZOE7GDZDP4XBNMC5Z6V5GIKAK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nGoogle轉軚 擬向傳媒買高質新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-HB5xeAf5FEBXSy7a5A5K6x5GRo=/640x358/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5N5H7U34RYHPYJVTIFUCTA54HY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-HB5xeAf5FEBXSy7a5A5K6x5GRo%3D%2F640x358%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5N5H7U34RYHPYJVTIFUCTA54HY.jpg&h=19c1a5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGoogle澳紐主管席爾瓦亦宣佈與澳洲多家小型傳媒集團達成付費協議。<br />\n<br />\n在多地政府與傳媒施壓下，美國搜尋器巨擘Google一改過往立場，前天宣佈有計劃向某些新聞機構，就平台展示的新聞內容付費，但未有公佈計算方式與金額等細節。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先在澳德巴西推行<br />\n<br />\nGoogle新聞產品管理副總裁本德前天在聲明指，「一個充滿活力的新聞行業很重要」，尤其在今天人們活在疫症大流行裏，又越來越關心種族平等議題，因此企業願意「為明年推出的嶄新新聞體驗」，就「高質素內容」付費，容許傳媒能以「內容牟利」。<br />\n<br />\n付費計劃將率先覆<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n設有訂閱收費的新聞資訊。<br />\n<br />\n科技巨企奪去傳媒重要的廣告收益問<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n制訂遊戲規則一方」，主宰着誰能參與遊戲、支付金額。<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"75556c9c74af49bccc10f50db434b0f9ed554bd9","tid":2081442,"uid":135740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:33:11.000Z","msg":"做下樣姐 人民幣咁香<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9yNA87k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9yNA87k.jpg&h=1f3e08bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"968d43ecb2165d43075f445c3c404f9e0096f6d4","tid":2081442,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:33:35.000Z","msg":"蘋果係咪有救"},{"pid":"6ae863e2044f01c5859ab450107bbb5ea1b19463","tid":2081442,"uid":144196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75556c9c74af49bccc10f50db434b0f9ed554bd9","tid":2081442,"uid":135740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:33:11.000Z","msg":"做下樣姐 人民幣咁香<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9yNA87k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9yNA87k.jpg&h=1f3e08bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:55:02.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔知google奶嚟做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正youtube google 嗰啲都冇得入大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />android 大陸夠薑咪咪L用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8459f48bbb656194e3da11fcccf2b5c114e66772","tid":2081442,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"買人民日報同環球時報d 高質新聞就夠"}]}